@startuml
' --- Configuración Visual ---
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam dpi 120

' Forzar que el motor sepa que es de componentes/despliegue
allowmixing

' Estilos base
skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #B0BEC5
    FontColor #263238
}

header Arquitectura CI/CD
footer DevOps - 2026

' --- Elementos ---
' Usamos la sintaxis más básica: component "Nombre" as ID
component "Developer\nLocal Env" as Dev #E3F2FD

rectangle "Automation_Zone" #F1F3F5 {
    component "GitHub_Repo" as GIT #D1D5DA
    component "GitHub_Actions" as CI #FFFFFF
}

component "Docker_Registry" as REG #B3E5FC

rectangle "Production_Zone" #F1F3F5 {
    component "Staging_Server" as STG #E8F5E9
    component "Production_Server" as PROD #FFEBEE
}

' --- Relaciones ---
Dev -right-> GIT : push
GIT -right-> CI : trigger

note bottom of CI
  Steps: Build & Test
end note

CI -down-> REG : push image

REG -down-> STG : pull
REG -down-> PROD : pull

' Colores de flechas directos
CI -[#blue]down-> STG : deploy dev
CI -[#red]down-> PROD : deploy main

@enduml